1. *Bolesna* je često imala glavobolje. (She was often sick with headaches.)
2. On je bio *bolesan* od malih nogu. (He was sickly since he was a child.)
3. *Boleš* li od sinusitisa? (Do you suffer from sinusitis?)
4. Ona je pregledala *bolesne* pacijente. (She examined the ill patients.)
5. On je bio *bolestan* od februara. (He was ill since February.)